      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition vehicle that shows beautifully inside and out. The paint, body, trim, and interior all present extremely well, with a clean, well-kept appearance throughout and no notable wear worth pointing out. It runs and drives exactly as it should, offering the kind of confidence and presentation buyers hope for in a top-tier example. If you\u2019re looking for a truly standout vehicle that has been very well maintained and needs nothing, this is one to see.",
